text: sumarise the wreck of the stella in Guernesiais in 3 lines Here is a summary of the wreck of the Stella in Guernsesiais: La Stélla, yvraun dla mer, eut un désastre & Les Hanols. Lestranjére, qui étoait en train de siéloigner, n'a pas pu éviter les rocs eta été détruite Translation: The Stella, which was at sea, had a disaster at Les Hanois. The stranger, who was trying to get away, could not avoid the rocks and was destroyed. Sources: 1.The Boreas disaster page 1 eng:txt (page -) () 2 Sermiacheriegfoc page )
